list.comment: Update for ggpk 3.2. Added new ggpk assets with new folder structure. Removed shaper orb assignment component and related items. Removed modal component. Maps are now generated by layered divs due to new ggpk content. Users are no longer limited to how many maps they are able to shape. Updated info descriptions. Unique maps are now tagged with "unique" boolean in mapstore.
